        "name": "debug_network",
        "description": "Debug network issues on a Rubix controller",
        "arguments": [
          {
            "name": "device_id",
            "description": "The device to debug",
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "symptom",
            "description": "What is happening (e.g. offline, slow, timeout)",
            "required": false
          }
        ],
        "body": "You are debugging a network issue on device **{{device_id}}**.\n\nSymptom: {{symptom}}\n\nFollow this checklist:\n1. Check if the device is online (use the device API)\n2. Check the device's IP and gateway configuration\n3. Ping the device gateway\n4. Check for recent error logs\n5. Verify MQTT broker connectivity\n6. Check network interface status\n\nReport findings and recommend a fix."
      }
    ],
